               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Śǝrʿāta mǝnkʷǝsǝnnā “The Order of the Monastic Profession” (attributed
                     to Jacob of Serug) (fols. 3ra-103va)&#xD; I-1) Prayer upon receiving the habit
                     (fols. 3ra-37vb)&#xD; I-2) Prayer upon receiving the girdle (fols.
                     38ra-44ra)&#xD; I-3) Prayer upon receiving the skull cap (fols. 44ra-58rb)&#xD;
                     I-4) Prayer upon receiving the robe (fols. 58rb-97va)&#xD; I-5) Concluding
                     rites (fols. 97va-103va)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-2; colophon.</summary>
